  <para style="h">AbaseFiliphi</para>
  <para style="toc1">Incwadi KaPhawuli KwabaseFiliphi</para>
  <para style="toc2">AbaseFiliphi</para>
  <para style="toc3">Flp</para>
  <para style="mt2">Incwadi KaPhawuli</para>
  <para style="mt1">KwabaseFiliphi</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Ohanjweni lwakhe lwesibili lokutshumayela ivangeli likaJesu kwabeZizweni umpostoli uPhawuli wancedisa ukusungula ibandla edolobheni leFiliphi (bona Imisebenzi 16.11-40), ilizwe lamabutho ayesethethe umhlalaphansi. AbaseFiliphi bakha ubungane loPhawuli njalo bamsekela impilo yakhe yonke. Bathi sebezwile ukuthi wayeseRoma eyisibotshwa, babuthanisa imali yokumsiza bayithumeza lomunye wabo, indoda eyayithiwa ngu-Ephafrodithusi. Ngokuya kwesikhathi uPhawuli wamthumela emuva lencwadi yokubonga abaseFiliphi ngobungane babo langoxhaso lwabo.</para>
  <para style="ip">UPhawuli wayekwazi ukuthi abaseFiliphi babekhangelane lokuphikiswa okukhulu, yikho wabacebisa esebenzisa impilo yakhe njengesibonelo ukuze bakwazi ukwamukela ubunzima ngenjabulo. <char style="qt">Ethangweni lwamabutho enkosi</char> okuyinkaba yomuzi kaKhesari, uPhawuli ngokukhululeka okukhulu wayebika umlayezo wobukhosi wokuthi uJesu uyiNkosi. Isifiso sikaPhawuli kwayikuthi abaseFiliphi bathole ithemba elifanayo njalo <char style="qt">babelesibindi sokufakaza ivangeli bengelakwesaba.</char></para>
  <para style="ip">Ngeculo elimnandi, uPhawuli ukhuthaza abaseFiliphi ukuthi babe lesimilo sesisebenzi njengoJesu. Akazange ahahabele indawo yakhe ephezulu kodwa wazehlisa lalapho esekhangelane lokufa, konke lokhu ekwenzela abanye. Le yindlela entsha yokuba ngumuntu evezwa ngumbuso kaNkulunkulu. Ikhaya lethu lisembusweni kaNkulunkulu ngakho ngokutshiseka okukhulu simelele ukuphenduka koMsindisi wethu. Yena uzaguqula imizimba yethu elesimo esiphansi ibe njengomzimba wakhe olenkazimulo owavuka ekufeni.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="PHP 1"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PHP 1:1"/>UPhawuli loThimothi, inceku zikaKhristu uJesu,</para>
  <para style="b" vid="PHP 1:1"/>
  <para style="p" vid="PHP 1:1">Lakubo bonke abangcwele kuKhristu uJesu eFiliphi kanye lababonisi labadikoni:<verse eid="PHP 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="PHP 1:2"/>Umusa lokuthula okuvela kuNkulunkulu uBaba leNkosini uJesu Khristu kakube kini.<verse eid="PHP 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukubonga Lokukhuleka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="PHP 1:3"/>Ngiyambonga uNkulunkulu wami izikhathi zonke lapho ngilikhumbula. <verse eid="PHP 1:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="PHP 1:4"/>Emikhulekweni yami yonke ngilikhulekela lonke, ngihlezi ngikhuleka ngokuthokoza <verse eid="PHP 1:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PHP 1:5"/>ngenxa yokuhlanganyela kwenu evangelini kusukela ngosuku lwakuqala kuze kube khathesi, <verse eid="PHP 1:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PHP 1:6"/>ngilethemba lokuthi lowo owaqalisa umsebenzi omuhle kini uzawuqhubekisela phambili kuze kube lusuku lukaKhristu uJesu.<verse eid="PHP 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="PHP 1:7"/>Kuqondile ukuthi ngicabange ngokunjalo ngenxa yenu lonke, njengoba ngilani enhliziyweni yami njalo lanxa ngibotshiwe kumbe ngivikela ivangeli loba ngiliqinisa, lonke lihlanganyela lami emuseni kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="PHP 1:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="PHP 1:8"/>UNkulunkulu angafakaza ukuthi lonke ngilifiselani ngothando lukaKhristu uJesu.<verse eid="PHP 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="PHP 1:9"/>Umkhuleko wami ngowokuthi uthando lwenu lwande kokuphela ekwazini lasekuzikeni kokuqedisisa <verse eid="PHP 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="PHP 1:10"/>ukuze lenelise ukubona okuhle njalo lihlambuluke lingabi lasici kuze kube lusuku lukaKhristu, <verse eid="PHP 1:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="PHP 1:11"/>ligcwele izithelo zokulunga ezibuya ngoJesu Khristu ekudunyisweni lasekubongweni kukaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="PHP 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubotshwa KukaPhawuli Kuqhubekelisa Ivangeli Phambili</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="PHP 1:12"/>Bazalwane, ngifuna ukuba lazi ukuthi okwenzakale kimi kusizile impela ekuqhubekeliseni ivangeli phambili. <verse eid="PHP 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="PHP 1:13"/>Ngalokho, sekube sobala kubo bonke abalindi besigodlo lakwabanye bonke ukuthi ngibotshelwe uKhristu. <verse eid="PHP 1:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="PHP 1:14"/>Ngenxa yokubotshwa kwami, abazalwane abanengi sebelethemba eNkosini njalo sebelesibindi esikhulu sokutshumayela ilizwi likaNkulunkulu bengelakwesaba.<verse eid="PHP 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="PHP 1:15"/>Kuliqiniso ukuthi abanye batshumayela uKhristu ngenxa yomona lombango kodwa abanye ngenxa yesifiso esihle. <verse eid="PHP 1:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="PHP 1:16"/>Laba benza lokhu ngothando bekwazi ukuthi ngifakwe lapha ukuba ngivikele ivangeli. <verse eid="PHP 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="PHP 1:17"/>Abakuqala batshumayela ngoKhristu ngokuzikhukhumeza, bengeqotho, becabanga ukuthi bangangidalela uhlupho ngisekubotshweni. <verse eid="PHP 1:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="PHP 1:18"/>Kodwa-ke, kusizani pho? Into eqakathekileyo yikuthi ngezindlela zonke, ingabe kuyinjongo engalunganga loba eyeqiniso, uKhristu uyatshunyayelwa. Njalo ngenxa yalokhu mina ngiyathokoza.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="PHP 1:18">Yebo, ngizaqhubeka ngithokoza, <verse eid="PHP 1:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="PHP 1:19"/>ngoba ngiyazi ukuthi ngemikhuleko yenu langosizo lukaMoya kaJesu Khristu, okwenzakale kimi kuzaletha ukukhululwa kwami. <verse eid="PHP 1:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="PHP 1:20"/>Ngokutshiseka ngilindele njalo ngithemba ukuthi angiyikuyangeka langayiphi indlela, kodwa ngizakuba lesibindi esaneleyo ukuze kuthi khathesi njengenjwayelo uKhristu uzakudunyiswa emzimbeni wami, loba ngokuphila kumbe ngokufa. <verse eid="PHP 1:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="PHP 1:21"/>Ngoba kimi, ukuphila kunguKhristu lokufa kuyinzuzo. <verse eid="PHP 1:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="PHP 1:22"/>Nxa ngingaqhubeka ngiphila emzimbeni, lokhu kuzakutsho umsebenzi olezithelo kimi. Kodwa-ke, kuyini engizakukhetha? Angazi! <verse eid="PHP 1:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="PHP 1:23"/>Ngiphakathi kwakho kokubili: Ngifisa ukusuka ngibe loKhristu, okungcono kakhulu; <verse eid="PHP 1:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="PHP 1:24"/>Kodwa kuyasweleka kakhulu kini ukuba ngibe ngilokhu ngiphila kulumzimba. <verse eid="PHP 1:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="PHP 1:25"/>Sengikholwe lokhu, ngiyakwazi ukuthi ngizakuba khona, njalo ngizaqhubeka ngilani lonke ngenxa yokuthuthuka kwenu lokuthokoza ekukholweni, <verse eid="PHP 1:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="PHP 1:26"/>ukuze kuthi ngokuba lani kwami futhi, ukuthokoza kwenu kuKhristu uJesu kuzakwanda ngenxa yami.<verse eid="PHP 1:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Impilo Efanele Ivangeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="PHP 1:27"/>Loba kusenzakalani, lina ziphatheni ngendlela efanele ivangeli likaKhristu. Ngakho, langabe ngiyeza ukuzalibona loba ngizwe nje kuphela ngani ngingekho, ngizakwazi ukuba liqinile ngaMoya munye, lilwela ukholo lwevangeli njengomuntu munye, <verse eid="PHP 1:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="PHP 1:28"/>kungekho kwethuswa langayiphi indlela yilabo abaliphikisayo. Lokhu kuyisibonakaliso kubo ukuthi bazachithwa, kodwa lina lizasindiswa nguNkulunkulu. <verse eid="PHP 1:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="PHP 1:29"/>Ngoba kunikelwe kini ngenxa kaKhristu kungasikukholwa kuye kuphela, kodwa lokumhluphekela, <verse eid="PHP 1:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="PHP 1:30"/>njengoba lilwisa hlupho lunye elabona ngilalo, lakhathesi liyezwa ukuba ngilokhu ngilalo.<verse eid="PHP 1:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="PHP 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="PHP 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukulingisela Ukuthobeka KukaKhristu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PHP 2:1"/>Nxa kukhona okukhuthazayo ngokuhlangana loKhristu, nxa kulenduduzo evela ethandweni lwakhe, nxa kulobudlelwano loMoya, nxa kulozwelo lesihawu, <verse eid="PHP 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="PHP 2:2"/>phelelisani intokozo yami ngokuba ngqondo nye, lilothando lunye, limunye emoyeni njalo linjongo yinye. <verse eid="PHP 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="PHP 2:3"/>Lingenzi lutho ngokuzikhukhumeza loba ukuziphakamisa okuyize. Kodwa ngokuthobeka khangelani abanye njengabangcono kulani <verse eid="PHP 2:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="PHP 2:4"/>lingazikhathaleli izifiso zenu lodwa kodwa likhathalele lezifiso zabanye.<verse eid="PHP 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="PHP 2:5"/>Ekuphilisaneni kwenu, isimo sengqondo yenu kumele sifanane lesikaKhristu uJesu,<verse eid="PHP 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="PHP 2:6"/>Yena okwathi ngemvelo enguNkulunkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:6">kacabanganga ukulingana loNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:6">kuyilutho olungafinyelelwa,<verse eid="PHP 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="PHP 2:7"/>kodwa wazithoba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:7">wathatha isimo senceku,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:7">yena elesimo somuntu.<verse eid="PHP 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="PHP 2:8"/>Wathi ebunjwe wabonakala njengomuntu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:8">wazehlisa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:8">walalela kwaze kwaba sekufeni,</para>
  <para style="q3" vid="PHP 2:8">ukufa kwasesiphambanweni!<verse eid="PHP 2:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="PHP 2:9"/>Ngakho-ke, uNkulunkulu wamphakamisela endaweni ephezulu kakhulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:9">wamnika ibizo elingaphezu kwamabizo wonke,<verse eid="PHP 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="PHP 2:10"/>ukuba amadolo wonke aguqe ebizweni likaJesu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:10">ezulwini lasemhlabeni kanye langaphansi komhlaba,<verse eid="PHP 2:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="PHP 2:11"/>lezindimi zonke zivume ukuthi uJesu Khristu uyiNkosi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="PHP 2:11">kube ludumo lukaNkulunkulu uYise.<verse eid="PHP 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukucwebezela Njengezinkanyezi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="PHP 2:12"/>Ngakho-ke, bangane bami abathandekayo, njengoba lihlezi lilalela kungayisikho ukuthi ngikhona kuphela kodwa ikakhulu nxa ngingekho, qhubekani lisebenzela ukusindiswa kwenu ngokwesaba langokuthuthumela <verse eid="PHP 2:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="PHP 2:13"/>ngoba nguNkulunkulu osebenzayo phakathi kwenu ukuba lifune njalo lenze okumthokozisayo.<verse eid="PHP 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="PHP 2:14"/>Yenzani konke kungela kusola kumbe ukuphikisana <verse eid="PHP 2:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="PHP 2:15"/>ukuze libe ngabantwana bakaNkulunkulu abangelasici labahlambulukileyo, abamsulwa phakathi kwesizukulwane esonakeleyo lesixhwalileyo, lina elicwebezela phakathi kwaso liletha ukukhanya emhlabeni <verse eid="PHP 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="PHP 2:16"/>ligagadlela ilizwi lokuphila. Ngalokho ngizazincoma ngosuku lukaKhristu ukuthi kangigijimelanga kumbe ngasebenzela ize. <verse eid="PHP 2:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="PHP 2:17"/>Kodwa lanxa ngithululwa njengomnikelo wokunathwa phezu komhlatshelo lenkonzo evela ekukholweni kwenu, ngiyathaba ngithokoza lani lonke. <verse eid="PHP 2:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="PHP 2:18"/>Ngakho-ke, lani njalo thabani lithokoze lami.<verse eid="PHP 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UThimothi Lo-Ephafrodithusi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="PHP 2:19"/>Ngiyethemba eNkosini uJesu ukuba ngizathuma uThimothi kini masinyane ukuba lami ngithokoze lapho ngisamukela izindaba ngani. <verse eid="PHP 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="PHP 2:20"/>Kangilaye omunye onjengaye, othakazelela inhlalakahle yenu ngobuqotho. <verse eid="PHP 2:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="PHP 2:21"/>Ngoba abantu bonke bazifunela okwabo, hatshi okukaJesu Khristu. <verse eid="PHP 2:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="PHP 2:22"/>Kodwa lina liyakwazi ukuthi uThimothi usezifakazele ngoba njengendodana eloyise usesebenze lami emsebenzini wevangeli. <verse eid="PHP 2:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="PHP 2:23"/>Ngakho-ke, ngithemba ngizamthuma masinyane lapho sengibonile ukuba izinto zingihambela njani. <verse eid="PHP 2:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="PHP 2:24"/>Njalo ngiyathemba eNkosini ukuthi lami uqobo ngizakuza masinyane.<verse eid="PHP 2:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="PHP 2:25"/>Kodwa ngibona kufanele ukuthi ngimthume kini futhi u-Ephafrodithusi, umzalwane wami, obambisane lami umsebenzi lolibutho kanye lami, oyisithunywa senu futhi, elamthumayo ukuthi angisize ngendingeko zami. <verse eid="PHP 2:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="PHP 2:26"/>Ngoba uyalilangatha lonke njalo ukhathazekile njengoba lezwa ukuthi wayegula. <verse eid="PHP 2:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="PHP 2:27"/>Ngempela wayegula njalo waphose wafa. Kodwa uNkulunkulu waba lesihawu kuye, kungayisikho kuye kuphela kodwa lakimi ukuba angiphephise osizini phezu kosizi. <verse eid="PHP 2:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="PHP 2:28"/>Ngakho-ke, ngitshisekela kakhulu ukumthuma ukuze kuthi lapho limbona futhi lithokoze lami ngikhathazeke okunganeno. <verse eid="PHP 2:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="PHP 2:29"/>Mamukeleni eNkosini ngokuthokoza okukhulu njalo libahloniphe abantu abanjengaye <verse eid="PHP 2:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="PHP 2:30"/>ngoba waphosa wafela umsebenzi kaKhristu, wafaka impilo yakhe engozini ukuze angiphe usizo elingangiphanga lona.<verse eid="PHP 2:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="PHP 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="PHP 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Akulathemba Emzimbeni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PHP 3:1"/>Okokucina, bazalwane, thokozani eNkosini! Akusihlupho kimi ukulilobela ngezinto ezifanayo futhi ngoba lokho kuyisivikelo kini. <verse eid="PHP 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="PHP 3:2"/>Qaphelani izinja lezo, abantu labo abenza okubi lalabo abalimaza umzimba. <verse eid="PHP 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="PHP 3:3"/>Ngoba thina yithi abokusokwa, thina esikhonza uNkulunkulu ngoMoya wakhe, esiziqhenya ngoKhristu uJesu njalo esingabeki ithemba kokwenyama <verse eid="PHP 3:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="PHP 3:4"/>lanxa nje mina ngokwami ngilezizatho zethemba elinjalo.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="PHP 3:4">Nxa kulomuntu ocabanga ukuthi ulezizatho zokuthemba okwenyama, mina ngilezinengi: <verse eid="PHP 3:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PHP 3:5"/>ngasokwa ngosuku lwesificaminwembili, ngingowako-Israyeli, owesizwana sakoBhenjamini, umHebheru wamaHebheru; ngokomthetho, ngingumFarisi; <verse eid="PHP 3:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PHP 3:6"/>ngokutshiseka, ngahlukuluza ibandla; ngokulunga okugxile emthethweni, angilacala.<verse eid="PHP 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="PHP 3:7"/>Kodwa loba kuyini okwakuyinzuzo kimi khathesi ngikubala njengokulahlekelwa ngenxa kaKhristu. <verse eid="PHP 3:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="PHP 3:8"/>Phezu kwalokho, konke ngikubona kuyize lapho kulinganiswa lobukhulu obumangalisayo bokwazi uKhristu Jesu iNkosi yami esengilahlekelwe yizinto zonke ngenxa yakhe. Ngikubona kuyimfucuza ukuze ngizuze uKhristu <verse eid="PHP 3:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="PHP 3:9"/>njalo ngitholakale kuye, ngingelakulunga okungokwami okuvelela emthethweni, kodwa lokho kungenxa yokukholwa kuKhristu, ukulunga okuvela kuNkulunkulu njalo okungokukholwa. <verse eid="PHP 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="PHP 3:10"/>Ngifuna ukumazi uKhristu lamandla okuvuka kwakhe ekufeni lobudlelwano bokuhlanganyela ekuhluphekeni kwakhe, ngibe njengaye ekufeni, <verse eid="PHP 3:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="PHP 3:11"/>ukuze ngenye indlela, ngithole ukuvuka kwabafileyo.<verse eid="PHP 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="PHP 3:12"/>Akusikuthi sengikuzuzile konke lokhu loba ukuthi sengiphelelisiwe kodwa ngilwisa ukuba ngibambe lokho uKhristu Jesu angibambela khona. <verse eid="PHP 3:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="PHP 3:13"/>Bazalwane, angikazibali njengosekubambile lokho. Kodwa yinye into engiyenzayo, ngiyakukhohlwa okusemuva ngizama ngamandla ukufinyelela kokuphambili, <verse eid="PHP 3:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="PHP 3:14"/>ngilwisa ukuthi ngiyefinyelela ekucineni ukuba ngithole umvuzo uNkulunkulu angibizela wona ezulwini ngoKhristu uJesu.<verse eid="PHP 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukulingisa Isibonelo SikaPhawuli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="PHP 3:15"/>Sonke thina esesiphelele kumele sikhangele izinto ngengqondo enjalo. Nxa kokunye licabanga ngokwehlukileyo, lalokho uNkulunkulu uzakwenza kucace kini. <verse eid="PHP 3:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="PHP 3:16"/>Kuphela nje kasiqhubekeni ngalokho esesikuzuzile.<verse eid="PHP 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="PHP 3:17"/>Bazalwane, hlanganyelani labanye ekulandeleni isibonelo sami, libananzelele labo abaphila ngokwesibonelo esalitshengisa sona. <verse eid="PHP 3:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="PHP 3:18"/>Ngoba, njengoba ngangihlala ngilitshela kuqala lakhathesi ngiyatsho futhi langezinyembezi ukuthi abanengi baphila njengezitha zesiphambano sikaKhristu. <verse eid="PHP 3:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="PHP 3:19"/>Isiphetho sabo yikubhubha, unkulunkulu wabo yisisu sabo, lodumo lwabo lusehlazweni labo. Ingqondo yabo isezintweni zasemhlabeni. <verse eid="PHP 3:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="PHP 3:20"/>Kodwa elethu ikhaya lisezulwini. Njalo simlindele ngokutshiseka uMsindisi evela khonale, iNkosi uJesu Khristu, <verse eid="PHP 3:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="PHP 3:21"/>yena okuzakuthi ngamandla amenza abeke izinto zonke ngaphansi kwakhe, uzaguqula imizimba yethu elesimo esiphansi ibe njengomzimba wakhe olenkazimulo.<verse eid="PHP 3:21"/></para>
  <chapter eid="PHP 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="PHP 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Isicelo Sokuma Ngesibindi Lokubambana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PHP 4:1"/>Ngakho-ke bazalwane bami, lina engilithandayo lengilikhumbulayo, liyintokozo yami lomqhele wami, kumele liqine kanjalo eNkosini bangane abathandekayo!<verse eid="PHP 4:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="PHP 4:2"/>Ngiyamncenga uYuwodiya loSintikhe ukuba bavumelane eNkosini. <verse eid="PHP 4:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="PHP 4:3"/>Ngiyakucela mhlobo wami oqotho, siza abesifazane labo abasebenza lami kanzima ngenxa yevangeli, kanye loKlementi labanye engisebenza labo, abalamabizo abo asencwadini yokuphila.<verse eid="PHP 4:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhuthaza Kokucina</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="PHP 4:4"/>Thokozani eNkosini kokuphela. Ngiyatsho futhi ngithi: Thokozani! <verse eid="PHP 4:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PHP 4:5"/>Ukuthobeka kwenu kakubonakale kubo bonke. INkosi isiseduze. <verse eid="PHP 4:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PHP 4:6"/>Lingakhathazeki kodwa ngazo zonke izikhathi bikani izicelo zenu kuNkulunkulu ngokukhuleka, ngokuncenga langokubonga. <verse eid="PHP 4:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="PHP 4:7"/>Ukuthula kukaNkulunkulu okudlula ukuqedisisa konke kuzabusa inhliziyo zenu lezingqondo zenu kuKhristu uJesu.<verse eid="PHP 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="PHP 4:8"/>Okokucina bazalwane, konke okuliqiniso, lokulesithunzi, lokulungileyo, lokuhlambulukileyo, lokuhle, lokubukekayo, nxa ulutho luluhle kakhulu loba lubongeka, cabangani ngezinto ezinje. <verse eid="PHP 4:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="PHP 4:9"/>Loba kuyini elikufundileyo loba elikwamukeleyo loba elikuzwileyo kuvela kimi, loba elikubonileyo kimi, kwenzeni. UNkulunkulu wokuthula uzakuba lani.<verse eid="PHP 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubonga Izipho Zabo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="PHP 4:10"/>Ngiyathokoza kakhulu eNkosini ngokuthi khathesi selize lavuselela ukungikhathalela kwenu. Impela kade likhathazeka kodwa lingelalo ithuba lokukubonakalisa. <verse eid="PHP 4:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="PHP 4:11"/>Kangitsho lokhu ngenxa yokuthi ngiyaswela ngoba sengafunda ukwaneliseka kuyo yonke imimo. <verse eid="PHP 4:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="PHP 4:12"/>Ngiyakwazi ukuba ukuswela kuyini njalo ngiyakwazi ukuba kuyini ukuba lokunengi. Sengafunda imfihlo yokwaneliseka kuzozonke izimo, langabe ngiyasutha loba ngilambile, loba ngilokunengi kumbe ngiswela. <verse eid="PHP 4:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="PHP 4:13"/>Ngingazenza zonke izinto ngaye onginika amandla.<verse eid="PHP 4:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="PHP 4:14"/>Kodwa kwakukuhle ukuthi lihlanganyele lami ekuhluphekeni kwami. <verse eid="PHP 4:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="PHP 4:15"/>Phezu kwalokho, lina bantu baseFiliphi liyakwazi ukuthi ensukwini elaqala ngazo ukwazi ivangeli ngesikhathi ngisuka eMasedoniya, akukho lalinye ibandla elahlanganyela lami endabeni yokupha lokwamukela ngaphandle kwenu kuphela; <verse eid="PHP 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="PHP 4:16"/>ngoba langesikhathi ngiseThesalonika langithumela usizo kanengi lapho ngidinga uncedo. <verse eid="PHP 4:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="PHP 4:17"/>Akusikuthi ngifuna isipho kodwa ngifuna okuzakuba yinzuzo kini. <verse eid="PHP 4:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="PHP 4:18"/>Sengamukele umvuzo ogcweleyo lodlulisileyo; ngiphiwe okwaneleyo njengoba khathesi sengamukele ku-Ephafrodithusi izipho elazithumelayo. Zingumnikelo wephunga elimnandi, umhlatshelo owamukelekayo lothokozisa uNkulunkulu. <verse eid="PHP 4:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="PHP 4:19"/>UNkulunkulu wami uzakugcwalisa konke ukuswela kwenu ngenkazimulo yenotho yakhe kuKhristu uJesu.<verse eid="PHP 4:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="PHP 4:20"/>Udumo kalube kuNkulunkulu uBaba kuze kube nini lanini. Ameni.<verse eid="PHP 4:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuvalelisa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="PHP 4:21"/>Bingelelani bonke abangcwele abakuKhristu.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="PHP 4:21">Abazalwane abalami bayalibingelela.<verse eid="PHP 4:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="PHP 4:22"/>Abangcwele bonke bayalibingelela, ikakhulu labo abangabendlu kaKhesari.<verse eid="PHP 4:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="PHP 4:23"/>Umusa weNkosi uJesu Khristu kawube lomoya wenu.<verse eid="PHP 4:23"/></para>
  <chapter eid="PHP 4"/>
</usx>
